{"tha-ap354:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap354:0.2":"Saddasannakavagga ","tha-ap354:0.3":"Yavakalapiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap354:1.1":"“Nagare arunavatiya, ","tha-ap354:1.2":"asim yavasiko tada; ","tha-ap354:1.3":"Panthe disvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap354:1.4":"yavakalapam santharim. ","tha-ap354:2.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap354:2.2":"sikhi lokagganayako; ","tha-ap354:2.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap354:2.4":"nisidi yavasanthare. ","tha-ap354:3.1":"Disva nisinnam vimalam, ","tha-ap354:3.2":"mahajhayim vinayakam; ","tha-ap354:3.3":"Pamojjam janayitvana, ","tha-ap354:3.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap354:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap354:4.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap354:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap354:4.4":"yavatthare idam phalam. ","tha-ap354:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap354:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap354:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap354:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma yavakalapiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap354:7.1":"Yavakalapiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}